'''分子結'''（molecular knot，也稱為knotane）為一種類似[[繩結|繩結]]的[[机械互锁分子结构|机械互锁分子结构]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Lukin|first1=Oleg|last2=Vögtle|first2=Fritz|title=Knotting and Threading of Molecules: Chemistry and Chirality of Molecular Knots and Their Assemblies|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|date=25 February 2005|volume=44|issue=10|pages=1456–1477|doi=10.1002/anie.200460312|pmid=15704147}}</ref>。[[三叶结|三叶结]]組態的分子結為[[手性|手性]]分子，至少有二個[[对映异构|对映异构]]，像[[DNA|DNA]]和一些特定蛋白都是自然生成的分子結。[[乳铁蛋白|乳铁蛋白]]和其線性的異構物有不同的性質。其他的[[化學合成|合成]]分子結因為其球狀外形及[[奈米|奈米]]尺寸，因此是[[奈米科技|奈米科技]]中潛在的建設方塊。第一個合成分子結是由Sauvage在1989年合成<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Dietrich-Buchecker|first1=Christiane O.|last2=Sauvage|first2=Jean-Pierre|title=A Synthetic Molecular Trefoil Knot|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition in English|date=February 1989|volume=28|issue=2|pages=189–192|doi=10.1002/anie.198901891}}</ref>。

knotane一詞是由Fritz Vögtle等在2000年在[[应用化学_(期刊)|应用化学期刊]]中創建，類似Rotaxane（[[轮烷|轮烷]]）、catenane（[[索烃|索烃]]）<ref>{{cite journal | author=Lukin O, Vögtle F | title=Knotting and Threading of Molecules: Chemistry and Chirality of Molecular Knots and Their Assemblies | journal=[[Angewandte_Chemie_International_Edition|Angewandte Chemie International Edition]] | volume=44 | issue=10 | year=2005 | pages=1456–1477 | pmid=15704147 | doi=10.1002/anie.200460312}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author=Safarowsky O, Nieger M, Fröhlich R, Vögtle F | title=A Molecular Knot with Twelve Amide Groups - One-Step Synthesis, Crystal Structure, Chirality | journal=[[Angewandte_Chemie_International_Edition|Angewandte Chemie International Edition]] | volume=39 | issue=9 | year=2000 | pages=1616–1618 | pmid=10820452 | doi=10.1002/(SICI)1521-3773(20000502)39:9<1616::AID-ANIE1616>3.0.CO;2-Y}}</ref>，不過[[IUPAC|IUPAC]]尚未核定此一詞語。

已發現許多合成分子結的方式<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Ashton|first1=Peter R.|last2=Matthews|first2=Owen A.|last3=Menzer|first3=Stephan|last4=Raymo|first4=Françisco M.|last5=Spencer|first5=Neil|last6=Stoddart|first6=J. Fraser|last7=Williams|first7=David J.|title=Molecular Meccano, 27. A Template-directed Synthesis of a Molecular Trefoil Knot|journal=Liebigs Annalen|date=December 1997|volume=1997|issue=12|pages=2485–2494|doi=10.1002/jlac.199719971210}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Rapenne|first1=Gwénaël|last2=Dietrich-Buchecker , and Jean-Pierre Sauvage *|first2=Christiane|last3=Sauvage|first3=Jean-Pierre|title=Copper(I)- or Iron(II)-Templated Synthesis of Molecular Knots Containing Two Tetrahedral or Octahedral Coordination Sites|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=February 1999|volume=121|issue=5|pages=1002–1015|doi=10.1021/ja982239+}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Feigel|first1=Martin|last2=Ladberg|first2=Rüdiger|last3=Engels|first3=Simon|last4=Herbst-Irmer|first4=Regine|last5=Fröhlich|first5=Roland|title=A Trefoil Knot Made of Amino Acids and Steroids|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|date=25 August 2006|volume=45|issue=34|pages=5698–5702|doi=10.1002/anie.200601111}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Guo|first1=Jun|last2=Mayers|first2=Paul C.|last3=Breault|first3=Gloria A.|last4=Hunter|first4=Christopher A.|title=Synthesis of a molecular trefoil knot by folding and closing on an octahedral coordination template|journal=Nature Chemistry|date=7 February 2010|volume=2|issue=3|pages=218–222|doi=10.1038/nchem.544}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Barran|first1=Perdita E.|last2=Cole|first2=Harriet L.|last3=Goldup|first3=Stephen M.|last4=Leigh|first4=David A.|last5=McGonigal|first5=Paul R.|last6=Symes|first6=Mark D.|last7=Wu|first7=Jhenyi|last8=Zengerle|first8=Michael|title=Active-Metal Template Synthesis of a Molecular Trefoil Knot|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|date=16 December 2011|volume=50|issue=51|pages=12280–12284|doi=10.1002/anie.201105012}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Carina|first1=Riccardo F.|last2=Dietrich-Buchecker|first2=Christiane|last3=Sauvage|first3=Jean-Pierre|title=Molecular Composite Knots|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=January 1996|volume=118|issue=38|pages=9110–9116|doi=10.1021/ja961459p}}</ref>。也已找到合成{{le|五葉結|pentafoil|五葉}}分子結的方式<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Ayme|first1=Jean-François|last2=Beves|first2=Jonathon E.|last3=Leigh|first3=David A.|last4=McBurney|first4=Roy T.|last5=Rissanen|first5=Kari|last6=Schultz|first6=David|title=A synthetic molecular pentafoil knot|journal=Nature Chemistry|date=6 November 2011|volume=4|issue=1|pages=15–20|doi=10.1038/nchem.1193|pmid=22169866}}</ref>。

